---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Build Your Rig ‚Äî Tebian">
	<main>
		<article class="doc">
			<h1>One ISO. Infinite Tools.</h1>
			<p class="lead">Why download a specialized distro when you can morph your system?</p>

			<section class="modes">
				<p>Tebian doesn't believe in "Gaming Distros" or "Security Distros." A distro is just a set of packages. Through the <code>fuzzel</code> menu, you can transform your Tebian installation into any specialized rig in seconds.</p>
				
				<div class="rig-grid">
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üëµ</span>
						<h3>Desktop (Familiar)</h3>
						<p>Perfect for newcomers. File manager, notifications, clipboard, screenshots, Bluetooth. Floating windows, focus-follows-mouse. Feels like home.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">Installer ‚Üí Desktop ‚Üí First Boot ‚Üí Desktop</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üíª</span>
						<h3>Desktop (Base)</h3>
						<p>For the elite. Just Sway, fuzzel, kitty, audio. You choose every single binary. Tiling by default. No forced extras.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">Installer ‚Üí Desktop ‚Üí First Boot ‚Üí Base</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üîê</span>
						<h3>Secure Server</h3>
						<p>SSH + UFW firewall + fail2ban + htop. Hardened, production-ready. Standard system utilities included.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">Installer ‚Üí Server ‚Üí Secure Server</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">‚ö°</span>
						<h3>Bare Server</h3>
						<p>SSH + pure Debian. Nothing else. The ultimate blank canvas. Build exactly what you need with apt.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">Installer ‚Üí Server ‚Üí Bare Server</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üéÆ</span>
						<h3>Gaming Mode</h3>
						<p>Installs Steam, GameMode, MangoHud, and optimized Vulkan drivers. Optimized for performance.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">fuzzel ‚Üí Software ‚Üí Gaming Mode</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üîí</span>
						<h3>Security Mode</h3>
						<p>Adds industrial-grade hardening (ufw, fail2ban) and pulls the best tools from Kali/Parrot.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">fuzzel ‚Üí Security ‚Üí Hardening</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üíª</span>
						<h3>Dev Mode</h3>
						<p>One-click environments for Rust, Go, Node.js, and Docker. Everything pre-configured.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">fuzzel ‚Üí Software ‚Üí Dev Mode</code>
					</div>
					<div class="rig-card">
						<span class="rig-icon">üé®</span>
						<h3>Creative Mode</h3>
						<p>Installs the production stack: OBS, Blender, Krita, and Inkscape. Calibrated for work.</p>
						<code class="rig-cmd">fuzzel ‚Üí Software ‚Üí Creative Mode</code>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="no-penalty">
				<h2>Zero Penalty</h2>
				<p>Unlike other distros, Tebian doesn't lock you in. Want to try Gaming Mode and then delete it? Every mode is tracked. Removing it leaves your base system exactly as it was. No leftover bloat. No broken dependencies.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="fuzzel-demo">
				<h2>The Universal Interface</h2>
				<p>You don't need to hunt for software in a slow "App Store." Everything happens through the <code>fuzzel</code> menu (Super + D). It is the fastest way to control a computer ever devised.</p>
			</section>
		</article>

		<div class="nav">
			<a href="/">‚Üê Home</a>
			<span class="nav-divider">|</span>
			<a href="/source">Source</a>
			<a href="/manifesto">Manifesto</a>
			<a href="/docs/architecture">Architecture</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.doc {
		max-width: 850px;
		width: 100%;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: var(--accent-color);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #9399b2;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #cdd6f4;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	.rig-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.rig-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.rig-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent-color);
		background: rgba(137, 180, 250, 0.03);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.rig-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.rig-card h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
		color: #bac2de;
	}

	.rig-card p {
		color: #9399b2;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.rig-cmd {
		display: block;
		background: #000;
		padding: 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		color: #a6e3a1;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-family: monospace;
		border: 1px solid rgba(166, 227, 161, 0.1);
	}

	.nav {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.nav a {
		color: #6c7086;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.nav a:hover {
		color: var(--accent-color);
	}

	.nav-divider {
		color: #313244;
	}
</style>